    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been an absolute joy to own. It's been really well-loved and looked after, so it's still running like a champ and looks great on the road! It's the perfect fit for anyone looking for a solid, reliable car that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure. Come take it for a spin\u2014I just know you\u2019re going to love how it feels behind the wheel!",
