    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This example is mechanically sorted, boasting a recently serviced double VANOS system and documented subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers crisp engagement, sending power to the rear wheels via the factory M-Variable differential lock. Suspension components remain tight with refreshed bushings, and the cooling system has been overhauled with a high-flow water pump. While showing minor cosmetic patina expected of a well-loved enthusiast vehicle, it remains a thermally efficient and dynamically superior machine ready for the canyon roads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
